{"tid":1462693,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[點都唔割] 搞機場係我地行得最靚嘅一步","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:43:23.000Z","uid":157419,"like":84,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c164d0ddecf90d8490058bb1f3b09e783a1463","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"香港機場有幾重要唔再多講，<br />\n癱瘓機場運作對香港經濟嘅打擊係難以估計。<br />\n而香港政府最睇重嘅係咩？就係經濟。<br />\n只要能夠堅持，唔洗太耐，<br />\n一個星期連續取消所有航班，哪怕每日只係幾粒鐘，<br />\n香港政府都一定唔會坐視不理。<br />\n<br />\n到時港共得兩個做法：<br />\n1. 係機場用武力清場<br />\n2. 跪低讓步<br />\n<br />\n前者佢真係做得出就係焦土。<br />\n係香港國際機場放催淚彈/開槍/速龍大搜捕，<br />\n大家估下會唔會有無辜遊客受到波及？<br />\n一定有，而受影響旅客數量肯定唔少。<br />\n用下腦都知香港國際機場無可能有一秒係冇旅客/少旅客。<br />\n各國領事館金睛火眼望住機場局勢，<br />\n一有咩事，政府唔需要負責交代？<br />\n其他國家仲會唔會放自己人民去一個風腥血雨嘅機場？<br />\n去到呢刻香港經濟基本上已經玩完。<br />\n到時就算政府依然唔讓步 ，但大家已經攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n搞香港機場係得兩個結果，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攬炒一鍋熟</span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府跪低讓步</span>。<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係要搞機場嘅原因，明未？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">If we burn, you burn with us</span>.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後想講，扔核彈都唔割。</span>"},{"pid":"58d065ee8274e72775e0a720a329d7cd9193baba","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59f955d8a95e7de8db20bb9a5431daa40f5888f4","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5ab299f8545bb4cb6b6cffdb11daa5b796534b7","tid":1462693,"uid":110109,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"今日有不足，都係因為我地冇綱領，冇方針係我地少人要點，呢個係我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集體問題</span></span></strong>，說好的塞爆結果冇人。<br />\n<br />\n解決問題係一齊解決。<br />\n唔係搵人出黎鬧。<br />\n<br />\n冇入黎就等於你冇contribute過。<br />\n指手劃腳不如你親自現場提出！<br />\n<br />\n依家就入黎，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好委屈左手足兄弟！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n班藍絲核爆都唔割，我地跌個銀仔就大呼小叫，係咪傻撚左？"},{"pid":"2ee7c0566930d422929998a77daf5c760e60c9f9","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec08d3761e49abd51d698aec4d3ab808a677316c","tid":1462693,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d8ef9b03c2398698bcd740a4f7b7c3eb6888f014","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:08:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc76aae13d11919b8c82f133eea9aa76366cc471","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a2f9419593830f1c2d6ebe09414113fe9ad900b0","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"大家同一條船 扔核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"6427c5e28a0b239f0f2484c1222960294c365064","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7fb493f19d2e0a9486d784c86cf5cb10551ae20c","tid":1462693,"uid":119173,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"今日真係叫人少咩?<br />\n叫果班一路坐係 Arrival Hall 既果班手足，上去 Departure Hall度支援啦。成件事就唔會好似而家咁唔湯唔水"},{"pid":"bb56519f1d7d57c72e951b4b748fa7c8298fefed","tid":1462693,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"要對付林鄭，要草船借箭，要借狗火力打大佬<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c5e210ca27a06a6c4bc0984a04ffbfde1fce1892","tid":1462693,"uid":274513,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"算尻數啦你<br />\n<br />\n真相就係香港人會覺得咁樣好肉酸<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解要阻人番屋企？<br />\n<br />\n比你係旅客都會係屌尻班細路，唔好咁天真以為佢地真係撐大家"},{"pid":"eb76b69659aaecee4ff13d340dec95e0ff84c95d","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fb493f19d2e0a9486d784c86cf5cb10551ae20c","tid":1462693,"uid":119173,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"今日真係叫人少咩?<br />\n叫果班一路坐係 Arrival Hall 既果班手足，上去 Departure Hall度支援啦。成件事就唔會好似而家咁唔湯唔水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"其實有去現場就知唔少<br />\n唔知出面班人係咪存心分化"},{"pid":"ffff0f932a257419b474e589875d57b1b3a4468a","tid":1462693,"uid":124330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b5ab299f8545bb4cb6b6cffdb11daa5b796534b7","tid":1462693,"uid":110109,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:17.000Z","msg":"今日有不足，都係因為我地冇綱領，冇方針係我地少人要點，呢個係我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集體問題</span></span></strong>，說好的塞爆結果冇人。<br />\n<br />\n解決問題係一齊解決。<br />\n唔係搵人出黎鬧。<br />\n<br />\n冇入黎就等於你冇contribute過。<br />\n指手劃腳不如你親自現場提出！<br />\n<br />\n依家就入黎，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好委屈左手足兄弟！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n班藍絲核爆都唔割，我地跌個銀仔就大呼小叫，係咪傻撚左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:11:59.000Z","msg":"612<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f397886a7253c7c6496fd6e4a79a702ffeb880","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44ca3801126dfd4312bf1b902f8b1fbfb9adec8a","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff275e1f138ed9e2a6bfd38775239539c69db901","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:14:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81964c0c337c78e1686628b7522130d6f4448547","tid":1462693,"uid":157419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":